text: Haldun Boysan (6 July 1958 – 31 August 2020) was a Turkish actor. He was born in Ankara. He was known for his roles as Kamil in On Board (1998), Fethi in Robbery Alla Turca (2005) and as Vasfi in The Jackal (2010).
